    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-strung S54B32 inline-six engine. This unit features individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable camshaft timing, providing an exceptional power band that pulls hard to the 8,000 RPM redline. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate selection, feeding power through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe mounting points have been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings were addressed as preventative maintenance. The suspension features refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the chassis's original torsional rigidity and neutral handling characteristics. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain is dialed in for the purist driver seeking a visceral, analog experience.",
