      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Lexus RX 350 in a stunning Eminent White Pearl. This vehicle has been our reliable family car and is in solid condition throughout. The exterior retains a beautiful luster, with only the expected minor stone chips on the front bumper from highway driving. The interior is finished in premium Stratus Gray leather; the seats are firm and supportive with no rips, though there is light creasing on the driver's side bolster. All technology features\u2014including the 12.3-inch multimedia display, 12-speaker premium sound system, and the suite of Safety System+ features\u2014are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is excellent. It has been serviced exclusively at the dealership every 5,000 miles, with a full log available. The 3.5L V6 engine runs smoothly, and the transmission shifts seamlessly. Recent maintenance includes a fresh oil change, new cabin air filters, and a set of Michelin tires installed less than 8,000 miles ago. This is a non-smoker, pet-free vehicle that has been garaged nightly. It\u2019s ready to provide its next owner with years of luxury and reliability.",
